title: You Dont Mess With The Zohan R5 LiNE XviD-KAMERA
description:
Genre: Action | Comedy
Year: 2008
Country: USA
Runtime: 113 min
User Rating: 5.6/10 (10,309 votes)
Director: Dennis Dugan
Cast: Adam Sandler, John Turturro, Emmanuelle Chriqui, Nick Swardson, Lainie Kazan, Ido Mosseri, Rob Schneider, Dave Matthews and many more ...

Plot:
This is the story about a Mossad agent Zohan Dvir, who fakes his death so he can re-emerge in New York City as a hair stylist. He romances his clients by giving them "special services" in the back room. However, he is eventually recognized, and risks losing his newfound life and career.
